程序包 io.github.moyusowo.neoartisanapi.api.recipe

接口 ArtisanCampfireRecipe

所有超级接口:
ArtisanFurnaceLikeRecipe, ArtisanRecipe
@NonExtendable public interface ArtisanCampfireRecipe extends ArtisanFurnaceLikeRecipe
Campfire cooking recipe interface, extending the base ArtisanRecipe.

Recipe features:

  • Supports custom cooking time (ticks)
  • Configurable experience output
  • Overrides vanilla MaterialChoice logic - vanilla MaterialChoice no longer applies!
